    public ResponseEntity<ConvertedDatatablesData<Department>> OrganizationsItemDepartmentsThymeleafController.datatablesByIdsIn(@RequestParam("ids") List<Long> ids, DatatablesColumns datatablesColumns, GlobalSearch search, DatatablesPageable pageable, @RequestParam("draw") Integer draw) {
        
        Page<Department> departments = getDepartmentService().findAllByIdsIn(ids, search, pageable);
        long totalDepartmentsCount = departments.getTotalElements();
        ConvertedDatatablesData<Department> data =  new ConvertedDatatablesData<Department>(departments, totalDepartmentsCount, draw, getConversionService(), datatablesColumns);
        return ResponseEntity.ok(data);
    }
    
